## 🚀 安装

### 方法 1：自动安装

```bash
./install.sh
```

### 方法 2：手动安装

```bash
# 克隆仓库
git clone https://github.com/fclwtt/openclaw-skills.git
cd openclaw-skills/skills/{{SKILL_NAME}}

# 复制到 OpenClaw skills 目录
cp -r . ~/.openclaw/skills/{{SKILL_NAME}}/
```

